Design a premium dark-mode fintech web application called 
"EthicaInvest" — an ethical robo-advisor built for the 
Indian retail investor.

COLOR SYSTEM:
- Page background: #0D1B2A (deep navy)
- Card background: #1A2B3C
- Primary accent / gains: #00F5A0 (electric green)
- Warning / drift: #F5A623 (amber)
- Danger / loss: #FF4D4D (red)
- Info / neutral: #00C2FF (teal)
- Saffron accent (Indian identity): #FF9933 
  (used sparingly on badges and highlights)
- Text primary: #FFFFFF
- Text secondary: #8899AA
- Font: Space Grotesk (headers) + Inter (body)
- All currency: Indian Rupee ₹ symbol, 
  Indian number format (lakhs/crores):
  ₹1,24,500 not $124,500
  Show "₹12.4L" for compact display

---

SCREEN 1 — ONBOARDING QUIZ

Full page centered card, max-width 560px.
Logo: "EthicaInvest" with Ashoka chakra-inspired 
leaf icon in electric green.
Tagline: "Invest smarter. Invest ethically."

4-step progress pill at top.

Step 1 — "What is your investment horizon?"
4 pill buttons:
"Less than 1 year" / "1–3 years" / 
"3–7 years" / "7+ years"

Step 2 — "What is your monthly SIP capacity?"
Slider from ₹500 to ₹1,00,000.
Show formatted value above thumb: "₹5,000/mo"
4 quick-select pills below: 
"₹500" / "₹2,000" / "₹5,000" / "₹10,000"

Step 3 — "How do you feel about market volatility?"
Slider 1–10. Left: "Avoid risk" / Right: "Grow fast"
Below slider: SEBI risk category auto-assigned:
"Based on your score: Moderately High Risk (SEBI)"

Step 4 — "Select your ethical framework"
3 tall toggle cards:
  - "ESG India" — leaf icon
    "Funds screened for environment, social & 
    governance by SEBI guidelines"
  - "Shariah" — crescent icon  
    "TASIS-certified Shariah-compliant Indian funds.
    No interest, alcohol, or tobacco exposure."
  - "Hybrid" — balance icon
    "Combines ESG + broad market exposure"

Step 5 — "Set your financial goal"
Goal type selector pills: 
"Retirement" / "Home" / "Education" / "Wealth"
Two inputs: "Target amount ₹" + "Target year"
Below: "Estimated SIP needed: ₹4,200/month"
(in electric green, auto-calculated)

CTA: "Build My Portfolio →" (full-width, green)

