GLOBAL NOTES:
- All numbers in Indian format: ₹1,24,500 
  (not ₹124,500)
- Compact: ₹1.2L, ₹3.6L, ₹1Cr
- Benchmark label: "Nifty 50" not "S&P 500"
- Regulatory badge on footer: 
  "SEBI Paper Portfolio · Not real money"
- Saffron (#FF9933) used only for 
  Shariah fund accents and goal milestones
- NSE/BSE exchange tags on all fund cards
- SIP language throughout (not "deposit")
- Mobile: 390px breakpoint — stat cards 
  collapse to 2x2 grid + scrollable